    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TO ANACOSTIA\nHELICOPTER ROTOR BLADES cast\nshadow\nover Washington,\nD.\nC.\nMAY 14, 15, 16, 17,\n1953",
      "The Ninth Annual Forum of the American Heli-\ncopter Society, held May 14-17, at Washing-\nton's\nMayflower Hotel,\nmarked the\nthird\nsuccessive year for convening in the Nation's\nCapital.\nThe first annual forum was held in\nPhiladelphia in 1945.\nThe fifth forum, 1949,\nwas in New York City.\nМЕНСОР O\nSOCIE\nDesigned and Donated by\nPREWITT\nAIRCRAFT COMPANY\nWorld's pioneer designer-producer of\nBonded Steel Rotor Blades for Helicopters\nCLIFTON HEIGHTS, PA.\nPOST CARD\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE"
    ],
